creator: Brose Group
descriptionHtml: The "myBrose" app keeps you up to date: Information about the company, the latest news and a selection of job offers are available to all interested parties. In addition, "myBrose" offers a login area for employees of the Brose Group. Here they find current information from their field of work - quickly and conveniently on their private smartphone.
descriptionShort: myBrose - stay in touch with the latest company news in the Brose Group.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• There is a new way to create posts directly and more quickly using the Post widget.
• On-demand translation is now also available for all widgets.
• Editors can now create content in Afrikaans, Malagasy, Mongolian and Zulu.
• The latest newsfeed and News Stage widget are now available for all. This includes endless scrolling, liking and commenting from the newsfeed, and more!
• On pages, bullet points did not match the text color. This has been fixed.

• The Chat interface is now fully accessible for users using screen readers.
